{"tid":2153064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日落樓打開信箱心都寒埋","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T06:37:02.000Z","uid":264040,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2508f37ea04bb81cd352bc80c8f1b3bbe4699611","tid":2153064,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"(借朋友ac出) <br />\n話説好日都唔會開信箱既我<br />\n今日走左去信箱收信<br />\n係一堆信件之中發現左一封特別野<br />\n<span class=\"red\">信封口用公仔貼紙封口嘅信</span><br />\n睇下地址又無錯<br />\n但係無話邊個收<br />\n我心諗封信係唔係去錯時空<br />\n今時今日已經無人再用卡通貼紙貼住信封口<br />\n我就好奇地打開一睇<br />\n雙手唔受控制一野掉開左<br />\n到我回神再走過去睇<br />\n發現<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n屌你係殘體字嘅國安法文宣<br />\n大概有4至5張紙<br />\n其中一張係封信<br />\n署名係「你的另一個香港家人上」<br />\n<br />\n又用殘體字寫我地址<br />\n又有郵政局印<br />\n表示好驚<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有無人都收到？</span><br />\n家住將軍澳某屋苑"},{"pid":"7e487c759fedb5e64da7766ea24cef0d1fb32d38","tid":2153064,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253948f5c5395ca39347007ea5587bb73e153096","tid":2153064,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d89573e439cce877cc912e80f1c96b1ec119bf","tid":2153064,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b689ff9d659e4041a4870222a8ed96f9c1e9e455","tid":2153064,"uid":296677,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:31:02.000Z","msg":"你的另一個香港家人上？<br />\n<br />\n家人？<br />\n你係私生子？ 定係失散多年兄弟姊妹？<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">遇騙案要報警啦</span>"},{"pid":"945742cef822c117d65f3e66590ae6a72f0b29aa","tid":2153064,"uid":